{
  "stem": "4276.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to regular school, six grades.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After six grades, I went to a Jewish gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I only had one year of schooling because then, the German walked in into Cracow, took over the Cracow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Jewish children had no right to go to school anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother gave them our-- one of our rooms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was few students that would come and learn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all the teachers from the school would come and teach us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was done so that nobody would see when we walked in or walked out, or something like that because this was not allowed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, right away when they got in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Cracow was not destroyed because Cracow had lots of beautiful churches and castle and lots of museums and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they didn't want to-- both, both sides didn't want to ruin it because there was some arts that they right away through took to Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They, I mean Germans, OK?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they really took apart one church-- and this was the biggest church in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had to have to store closed for a few days, but then my mother opened it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was the one that knew where merchandise was from being always in the store.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every day after the school, I would say, hi, Dad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "May I come in?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then my father volunteered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was an officer in Polish army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And because of his surgeries, they released him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He didn't have to go to war, but he volunteered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was the last time I saw my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My was taken-- my brother left the house with his uncles toward Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
